snippet.title: We Are OFK - Title Sequence
snippet.description:
From indie pop band OFK: this video game's story follows the lives of four friends in their 20s as they attempt to break into the music business, fall in and out of love, and figure out how to pay rent and make art in Los Angeles. Out Now on Steam, PlayStation & Nintendo Switch! http://ofk.cool/steam

•   Play on Steam: http://ofk.cool/steam
•   Stream "Follow/Unfollow" by OFK everywhere: http://ofk.cool/music
•   Twitter: https://twitter.com/OFKband
•   Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ofkband
•   Website: http://ofk.cool

Title Sequence animation by Six Point Harness https://www.sixpointharness.com/
We Are OFK original score composed and performed by Omniboi https://omniboi.bandcamp.com/
Mixed by Jorel Corpus https://jorelcorp.us/
Mastered by Jett Galindo https://linktr.ee/jettgalindo
